<style>
  @import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Newsreader:ital,opsz,wght@0,6..72,400;0,6..72,600;0,6..72,700;1,6..72,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;700&display=optional");

  :root {
    --paper: #f4f1e8;
    --ink: #1a1714;
    --muted: #6b655c;
    --ruby: #da291c;
    --rule: #cfc8b8;
    --paper-2: #fbf9f2;
  }

  *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html, body {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: "Newsreader", Georgia, serif;
    line-height: 1.55;
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
  .mono { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; }

  .layout {
    max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1.5rem;
    border-left: 1px solid var(--rule); border-right: 1px solid var(--rule);
    background: var(--paper-2);
  }

  .topbar {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: baseline;
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 3px double var(--ink);
  }
  .topbar .brand { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .topbar .meta {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.58rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
  }

  .stamp {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace;
    font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ruby);
    border: 1.5px solid var(--ruby);
    display: inline-block; padding: 4px 9px; transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
    margin: 1.75rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero { padding: 0.5rem 0 2.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 7vw, 5rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 0.98;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0.5rem 0 1.25rem; max-width: 16ch;
  }
  .hero h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ruby); }
  .hero p.lead { font-size: 1.25rem; max-width: 60ch; color: var(--ink); }
  .hero p.sub {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.72rem; line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--muted); max-width: 70ch; margin-top: 1.25rem;
  }
  .hero .redact { background: var(--ink); color: var(--ink); border-radius: 2px; padding: 0 2px; }
  .hero .redact:hover { color: var(--paper-2); }

  .figures { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  @media (max-width: 720px) { .figures { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); } }
  .fig { padding: 1.25rem 1.25rem 1.25rem 0; border-right: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .fig:nth-child(4n) { border-right: none; padding-right: 0; }
  @media (max-width: 720px) { .fig:nth-child(2n) { border-right: none; } }
  .fig .v { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .fig .v.red { color: var(--ruby); }
  .fig .k { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.56rem; letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 0.3rem; }

  .section-label {
    padding: 1.75rem 0 0.75rem;
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em;
    text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); margin-bottom: 0;
  }
  .section-label::before { content: "§ "; color: var(--ruby); }

  .apps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .app {
    padding: 2.25rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 64px 1fr 360px; gap: 2rem; align-items: start;
  }
  @media (max-width: 860px) { .app { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 1.1rem; } }

  .app .num { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-weight: 700; font-size: 2.4rem; line-height: 0.85; color: var(--ruby); }
  .app .body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.7rem; }
  .app .body .title { font-size: 1.9rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.05; }
  .app .body .tagline { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.78rem; color: var(--ruby); }
  .app .body .desc { font-size: 1.02rem; color: var(--ink); }

  .app .right { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.6rem; }
  .app .shot { display: block; aspect-ratio: 16/10; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--ink); background: var(--paper); }
  .app .shot img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; object-position: top; }
  .app .ctas { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); border: 1px solid var(--ink); }
  .btn {
    text-align: center; padding: 0.5rem 0.4rem; border-right: 1px solid var(--ink);
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.62rem; letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; color: var(--ink); transition: background 0.12s, color 0.12s;
  }
  .btn:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .btn:hover { background: var(--ruby); color: var(--paper-2); }
  .prompt-link { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.66rem; text-decoration: underline; color: var(--muted); }
  .prompt-link:hover { color: var(--ruby); }
  .fork-note {
    font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.66rem; line-height: 1.5; color: var(--muted);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--ruby); padding-left: 0.6rem; margin-top: 0.2rem;
  }

  .epilogue { padding: 2.5rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); }
  .epilogue h2 { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.6rem; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .epilogue h2::before { content: "§ "; color: var(--ruby); }
  .epilogue p { font-size: 1.12rem; max-width: 68ch; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .epilogue p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .epilogue .hl { color: var(--ruby); font-style: italic; }
  .epilogue .src { font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.66rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; }
  .epilogue .src a { text-decoration: underline; }
  .epilogue .src a:hover { color: var(--ruby); }

  footer.term-footer {
    padding: 1.25rem 0; font-family: "JetBrains Mono", monospace; font-size: 0.58rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted);
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  footer.term-footer a:hover { color: var(--ruby); }
</style>

<div class="layout">
  <header class="topbar">
    <a class="brand" href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">VIBES.DIY</a>
    <span class="meta">Rip City · By The Numbers · est. 2026</span>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <span class="stamp">⚠ Contains Publicly Available Numbers</span>
    <h1>Rip City, <em>by the numbers</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      The City of Portland is being asked to put up to a billion dollars into a privately operated arena whose owner pays one dollar a year in rent. We made three interactive toys out of the public figures. Apparently this counts as taking a side now.
    </p>
    <p class="sub">
      For legal and emotional safety we must disclose: every figure below comes from the city's own VSG study, the legislative record on SB 1501, or the <span class="redact">ripcitynotripoff.com</span> campaign. We simply put them on charts. Reader discretion is, evidently, advised.
    </p>
  </section>

  <div class="figures">
    <div class="fig"><div class="v">$4.25B</div><div class="k">Team sale price, Mar 2026</div></div>
    <div class="fig"><div class="v red">$1 / yr</div><div class="k">Rent the owner pays</div></div>
    <div class="fig"><div class="v">$1.02B</div><div class="k">20-yr public commitment</div></div>
    <div class="fig"><div class="v red">$0</div><div class="k">Owner's renovation share</div></div>
  </div>

  <div class="section-label">Exhibits — three ways to look at the same deal</div>

  <section class="apps">
    {{#each apps}}
      <article class="app">
        <div class="num">{{num}}</div>
        <div class="body">
          <h2 class="title">{{title}}</h2>
          <span class="tagline">{{tagline}}</span>
          <p class="desc">{{desc}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="right">
          <a class="shot" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}" aria-label="{{title}} screenshot"><img src="https://{{slug}}--{{author}}.prod-v2.vibesdiy.net/screenshot.jpg" alt="{{slug}}" onerror="this.onerror=null; this.src='{{@root.assetPrefix}}images/og-preview.png';"/></a>
          <div class="ctas">
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/vibe/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Open</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}?skipChat=true">Clone</a>
            <a class="btn" href="https://vibes.diy/remix/{{author}}/{{slug}}">Remix</a>
          </div>
          <a class="prompt-link" href="https://vibes.diy/chat/prompt?prompt64={{prompt64 desc}}">// or start fresh from this prompt</a>
          {{#if fork}}<p class="fork-note">{{fork}}</p>{{/if}}
        </div>
      </article>
    {{/each}}
  </section>

  <div class="epilogue">
    <h2>The Footnote Nobody Asked For</h2>
    <p>
      None of these numbers are secret. The city paid a firm to study what the arena actually needs — about <span class="hl">$253 million</span> — and the public ask came back closer to <span class="hl">$600 million</span>. The claimed "$670M economic impact" is gross output; the tax revenue the study could actually find was <span class="hl">$17.9 million a year</span>. Every peer city that handed over public money got <em>something</em> back — rent, a cut of the suites, a penalty if the team leaves. The proposal on the table gets Portland a building it already owns and a tenant who pays a dollar.
    </p>
    <p>
      We are not telling you what to think. We are telling you what the spreadsheet says, which has somehow become the controversial part. <span class="hl">Clone any of the three</span> and put your own numbers in — that is the whole point of a database you can open.
    </p>
    <p class="src">
      Sources: <a href="https://www.ripcitynotripoff.com/">ripcitynotripoff.com</a> · Portland VSG facilities study · Oregon SB 1501 / SB 5701 legislative record · <a href="https://www.opb.org/article/2026/02/26/oregon-funding-aging-moda-center/">OPB</a> · <a href="https://www.kgw.com/article/news/investigations/blazers-fans-call-moda-center-deal-a-ripoff/283-e80005d3-4223-4012-8c27-89efa15fb98b">KGW</a>. Figures reflect the campaign's framing; ranges are theirs. Votes scheduled Aug 12 and Dec 17, 2026.
    </p>
  </div>

  {{> newsletter}}

  <footer class="term-footer">
    <span>Vibes.diy · <a href="https://links.vibes.diy/homepage">homepage</a> · <a href="/expressions/">expressions</a></span>
    <span>// End of exhibits</span>
  </footer>
</div>
